### Describe the bug

I have an Entity with an EmbeddedId and an ElementCollection: 
```
@Entity()
public class MyEntity {
    @EmbeddedId
    EmbeddableId id;

    public String name;

    @ElementCollection
    public Set<EmbeddableElement> elementCollection = new HashSet<>();
}
```
```
@Embeddable
public class EmbeddableElement {
    public String name;
}
```

The embedded id has an composite key
```
@Embeddable
public class EmbeddableId  {
    public String id1;
    @ManyToOne
    public PartOfIdEntity id2;
}
```
```
@Entity()
public class PartOfIdEntity  {
    @Id
    public Long id;
}
```


### Expected behavior

No Exception when accessing the ElementCollection like in Quarkus 2.*

### Actual behavior

I get an Exception

Now if i access the elementCollection of MyEntity i get following exception: 
