### How to Reproduce?

1. Persist some data 
```
PartOfIdEntity partOfIdEntity = new PartOfIdEntity();
            partOfIdEntity.id = 1L;
            entityManager.persist(partOfIdEntity);

            MyEntity myEntity = new MyEntity();
            myEntity.id = new EmbeddableId();
            myEntity.id.id1 = "123";
            myEntity.id.id2 = partOfIdEntity;

            EmbeddableElement el = new EmbeddableElement();
            el.name = "abc";
            myEntity.elementCollection.add(el);
            entityManager.persist(myEntity);
```
2. Close the transaction
3. Access the data:
```
 MyEntity entityFromSelect = em.createQuery("SELECT e FROM MyEntity e", MyEntity.class).getSingleResult();
        entityFromSelect.elementCollection.size();

        // Cannot invoke "org.hibernate.sql.results.graph.entity.EntityInitializer.getNavigablePath()" because "firstEntityInitializer" is null:
        assertEquals(1, entityFromSelect.elementCollection.size());
```

